answers.body_markdown:
According to this [document][1] you can use following method :

    setImplicitTimeout(5, SECONDS);

and for resetting the global timeout : 

    resetImplicitTimeout();

 

  [1]: http://thucydides.info/docs/serenity-staging/#_working_with_timeouts

